{
  "stem": "22869.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Schooling, since we had no yeshivas, as they are known today, we had two kinds of schools.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had the cheder, which was the Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when you were a little bit bigger, you used to go to a yeshiva, was the higher-- higher learning establishments.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other ones, the other half a day, was public schools.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was obligatory, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for eight years, everybody had to attend public schools.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went together, boys and girls, Jews and non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it wasn't very pleasant for the Jewish person to attend a mixed school, since they were all Catholic, of course.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Jewish people, especially the ones who were in their appearance different than the modern Jew or the non-Jew, were usually mocked and laughed at.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a lot of times, also subjects to beatings by the non-Jewish peers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How about you, personally?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you experience anything like that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have experienced, many, many times, abuse in-- in-- in-- in the school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Especially by-- when we had these obligatory prayers in the morning, school prayers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in every class there was a crucifix.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, we were excused from praying, or-- or-- or saying something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nevertheless, the majority of the kids in the class were always mocking us for not keeping up with them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we also had, of course, teachers who were so anti-Semitic-- personally, many of my friends who had side curls-- which are called in Jewish, payots-- were a lot of times pulled by the teachers as a punishment.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't have to tell you what pain that causes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were subjected to abuse because of our Jewishness, without any doubt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a very, very strict Orthodox Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would even call him fanatic to an extent.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
